---
title: Chicken Tagine with Couscous and Chickpeas
description: André is well known for his jaunts to Morocco. Last time he returned he cooked up this recipe and everyone loved it! Tagines normally take hours and hours in a clay pot, but not this one... 20 minutes and a couple of pans and BAM... you could almost be in Morocco!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-tagine-af60e4d1-ce451391.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/chicken-tagine-5a74b1de30006c21fe6e92f2-13f91514.pdf
